// preset (B = D / Ly = 2 / 20 = 5 %). Topology copied from the OpenFOAM
// 11 tutorial incompressibleFluid/offsetCylinder; the outer bounding box
// is enlarged and made symmetric so the blockage matches AeroLab and the
// cross-validation comparison is honest.
//
//   x in [-20, +40]   (10 D upstream, 20 D downstream)
//   y in [-20, +20]   (10 D each side, B = 5 %)
//   z in [-1, +1]     (single span cell, empty BCs - quasi-2D)
