// Inner ring vertices sit on a circle r = 1 (cylinder) and r = sqrt(2)
// approx 1.414 (middle O-grid). Those numbers (1, 0.707107, 1.4,
// 0.989949) are unchanged from the tutorial -- only the outer bounding
